window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>The Detective</i> takes place from roughly March 2683 to March 2684. Where applicable, the chapters are named to map to the action in <i>The All-Pro</i> (book III in the Galactic Football League series). The story actually begins, however, on unknown dates during book II, <i>The Starter</i>. </p> <p>In terms of the GFL timeline, <i>The Detective</i> runs from roughly week seven of the 2683 regular season in <i>The Starter</i> through week 10 of the 2684 regular season in <i>The All-Pro</i>. </p>"; 
